#. <section class="sutta" id="sn47.39"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn47.39:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 47"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 47"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn47.39:0.2"
msgid "4. Ananussutavagga"
msgstr "4. Not Learned From Anyone Else"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn47.39:0.3"
msgid "39. Bhāvanāsutta"
msgstr "39. Development"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.183"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn47.39:1.1"
msgid "“Catunnaṃ, bhikkhave, satipaṭṭhānānaṃ bhāvanaṃ desessāmi."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I will teach you the development of the four kinds of "
"mindfulness meditation."

msgctxt "sn47.39:1.2"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha."
msgstr "Listen …"

msgctxt "sn47.39:1.3"
msgid "Katamā, bhikkhave, catunnaṃ satipaṭṭhānānaṃ bhāvanā?"
msgstr ""
"And what is the development of the four kinds of mindfulness meditation?"

msgctxt "sn47.39:1.4"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kāye kāyānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā, "
"vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant meditates by observing an aspect of the body—keen, "
"aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world."

msgctxt "sn47.39:1.5"
msgid "vedanāsu … pe …"
msgstr "They meditate observing an aspect of feelings …"

msgctxt "sn47.39:1.6"
msgid "citte … pe …"
msgstr "mind …"

msgctxt "sn47.39:1.7"
msgid ""
"dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke "
"abhijjhādomanassaṃ."
msgstr ""
"principles—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the "
"world."

msgctxt "sn47.39:1.8"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, bhikkhave, catunnaṃ satipaṭṭhānānaṃ bhāvanā”ti."
msgstr "This is the development of the four kinds of mindfulness meditation.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn47.39:1.9"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
